'''围盘树科'''又名[[周位花盘科|周位花盘科]]、[[巴西肉盘科|巴西肉盘科]]或[[团花盘树科|团花盘树科]]，共有3[[属|属]]9[[种|种]]，其中两属为单种属，生长在[[南美洲|南美洲]]的[[热带|热带]]地区；''Soyauxia'' 属生长在[[非洲|非洲]]。<ref name="a">Soltis, D. E.; Clayton, J. W.; Davis, C. C.; Gitzendanner, M. A.; Cheek, M.; Savolainen, V.; Amorim, A. M.; Soltis, P. S. (2007):Monophyly and relationships of the enigmatic family Peridiscaceae. ''Taxon'' 56(1):65-73.</ref>

本科[[植物|植物]]为[[乔木|乔木]]；单[[叶|叶]]互生，叶大，革质，有托叶；[[花|花]]两性，[[花萼|花萼]]有毛，[[花瓣|花瓣]]4-7；[[果实|果实]]为[[核果|核果]]。

== 属 ==
*''[[Peridiscus|Peridiscus]]'' [[Benth.|Benth.]]
*''[[Soyauxia|Soyauxia]]'' [[Oliv.|Oliv.]]
*''[[Whittonia|Whittonia]]'' [[Sandwith|Sandwith]]

1981年的[[克朗奎斯特分类法|克朗奎斯特分类法]]将其列在[[堇菜目|堇菜目]]，1998年根据[[基因|基因]]亲缘关系分类的[[APG_分类法|APG 分类法]]认为其无法放在任何一个[[目_(生物)|目]]中，属于系属不清的[[科|科]]，2003年经过修订的[[APG_II_分类法|APG II 分类法]]将其列在[[金虎尾目|金虎尾目]]。<ref name="a"/><ref name="b">{{cite journal|author = Davis, C. C. & Chase, M. W.|year = 2004|title = Elatinaceae are sister to Malpighiaceae; Peridiscaceae belong to Saxifragales.|journal = American Journal of Botany|volume = 91|pages = 262–273|url = http://www.amjbot.org/cgi/reprint/91/2/262|format = [[PDF|PDF]]|accessdate = 2007-07-01|archive-date = 2007-09-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070926223428/http://www.amjbot.org/cgi/reprint/91/2/262|dead-url = no}}</ref>
<ref name="c">{{cite book| last = Kubitzki| first = K.(Editor)| title = The Families and Genera of Vascular Plants Vol. 9| publisher = Springer-Verlag | date = 2007| location = Berlin, Germany| isbn = 978-3-54032214-6}}</ref>

